## Fetch Account Categories (type: 'account')

Account categories power store/seller browsing — different from listing categories.

```tsx
const { data } = useGetCategoriesQuery({ type: 'account', page: 1 })

const accountCategories = data?.categories ?? []

// Route for account category browsing (uses /a/ prefix by convention)
const href = { pathname: '/a/[slug]', query: { slug: getCategorySlug(category) } }
```

