## Prefetch Categories (App Startup)

Prefetch the category list at app root so the nav renders instantly without a loading state.

```tsx
// In src/app/App.tsx or a top-level layout component

import { useGetCategoriesQuery } from '@/state/categories/api'

function AppInitializer() {
  // Prefetch with no args — result is cached for 5 min and reused everywhere
  useGetCategoriesQuery({ page: 1 })
  return null
}
```

